User Stories - GlobalMart

US1
As a new user, I want to register with my email so that I can create an account and start shopping.

US2
As a registered user, I want to log in securely so that my account and personal information stay safe.

US3
As an international student, I want to see product prices in my home currency so that I know exactly how much I'm spending.

US4
As a shopper, I want to search for products by keyword so that I can quickly find what I need.

US5
As a browser, I want to add items to a shopping cart so that I can purchase multiple items at once.

US6
As a price-conscious buyer, I want to compare prices from different sellers so that I can get the best deal.

US7
As a cautious shopper, I want to read user reviews so that I know if a product is reliable.

US8
As a buyer, I want to track my order's shipping status so that I know when my package will arrive.

US9
As a shopper, I want to save items to a wishlist so that I can buy them later when I have money.

US10
As a non-Chinese speaker, I want to toggle between English and Chinese so that I can understand product descriptions.
